{"tid":1243334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇21號將目標對準警總？","createTime":"2019-06-19T11:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T14:16:23.000Z","uid":194177,"like":26,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8f847517ae1d0298f08616ba4bd0f4b302abdd","tid":1243334,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"而家再執住個撤字嚟講<br />\n外媒同無腦港豬都唔想理你<br />\n唔會再引起到任何注意<br />\n<br />\n但警權過大有幾大問題出面好多post有講<br />\n咁係咪應該將目標對準警總？<br />\n而家幾個訴求都同警察有關<br />\n加上警權過大係果日上街果200萬人都認同嘅<br />\n如果捉住呢一點<br />\n大家會有返個凝聚力<br />\n好似69前大家目標清晰要撤回咁<br />\n<br />\n再加上如果今次有機制可以管住班狗<br />\n佢地打9人都唔敢咁大力<br />\n更重要係削佢地士氣<br />\n慢慢產生離心<br />\n<br />\n有關警權過大幾個訴求：<br />\n1. 每個警員都必須清晰顯示警員號碼<br />\n2. 追究開槍責任，追究使用無理武力責任<br />\n3. 必須人為此下台<br />\n4. 可再補充<br />\n<br />\n點睇？"},{"pid":"c145feffeedfc8e536f476dcfef527ddceb2ac15","tid":1243334,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d215710f29801d0921b4b61013a616448e368a","tid":1243334,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d6df02a79ba1f5a52bfe9c2a63df628d5b344d","tid":1243334,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b362117a47529b9728a7347a6ca8f4516f192e84","tid":1243334,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168b1215e96e865077503653231c2db4b48f2828","tid":1243334,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e752b5505493912417238bb1a7